            "text": "Interpretation gate: pass only if a fine, persistent precipitate forms and pH lands in the 6.0–8.0 verification window. Out-of-range readings or unstable solids must be corrected before completion.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Pass: precipitate is stable and pH is 6.0–8.0.",
